\]

\end_inset

This says that the quadratic lower bound improves a lot whenever 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\mu}{2}\|c_{A}-c_{B}\|^{2}\gg v_{B}-v_{A}$
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\mu}{2}\|c_{A}-c_{B}\|^{2}\ll v_{B}-v_{A}$
\end_inset

.
